<!-- KNITR_ASIS_OUTPUT_TOKEN -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->

```r
cytoVirus %>%
  left_join(.,enrollment_data) %>%
  filter(cytokine %in% corsigage) %>%
  mutate(log2cyt = log2(value)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = age,
             y = log2cyt,
             color = cytokine)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_smooth(aes(fill = cytokine),
              method= \lm\") +
